      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Abu Ali Al Ashary, from Al Hassan Bin Ali Al Kufy, from Ubeys Bin Hisham, form Husayn Bin Ahmad Al Minqary, from Yunus Bin Zabyan, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘From the Sunnah, is wearing of the ring’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "3. Abu Ali al-Ash‘ariy has narrated from al-Hassan ibn Ali al-Kufiy from ‘Ubays ibn Hisham from Husayn ibn Ahmad al-Minqariy from Yunus ibn Zabayan who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Wearing the ring (insignia) is of the noble tradition.’” "
        ]
      }
